high_descs: Turn right and go diagonally across the kitchen, to the corner of the counter between the sink and ovens.
Get the head of lettuce from the counter.
Move to your left, to face the fridge.
Chill the lettuce on the center of the top fridge shelf, then take it back out.
Go to the counter to your right.
Put the lettuce on the counter, near the left front corner of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce on a kitchen counter.

high_descs: turn left and head for the fridge
place the lettuce to cool and then take it out
place the lettuce on the pavement
anns.task_desc: place a cold lettuce on the pavement

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left and move forward to face the counter.
Pick up the lettuce on the counter.
Step to the left to face the fridge.
Cool the lettuce in the fridge and then remove it.
Turn right and walk forward to face the corner of the counter.
Place the lettuce back on the counter in it's original position.
anns.task_desc: Cool a head of lettuce as well as put it back in the spot it came from.
